\p{Let #{G} be a [[gr-000G]] and #{X} be a nonempty set. Suppose #{G} [acts](gr-004Y) on #{X}. Then for each #{x\in X}, the [cardinality](nst-002B) of the [[gr-004B]] #{G\cdot x} is equal to the [index](gr-003J) of the [[gr-004C]] of #{x},
##{\Index{G}{\Stabilizer{G}{x}}=|G\cdot x|.}
